rComments: Dr Lehnherr provides students with excellent course material and clear informative lectures. His lecture style along with his Hot looks ;) make it quite easy to stay focused. I would take course from him again as I came out of the course with a wealth of new information, I really enjoy when he references his Arctic research.
Easy A, Would take again in order to get a 4.0 easy, notes are all on power point.
Great guy who give lots of extra credit opportunities ( 7% extra on your overall). Nice guy who knows his material.

He's a good professor and quite approachable. Everything that you need to know is on the powerpoint slides, so you don't need to read the textbook. He explains everything quite well and his slides are pretty informative. You don't necessarily have to attend every lecture in order to do well.

The lectures can feel a bit long but he is overall a good prof and nice person. Tests are fair. You only need to study from lecture slides. The labs can get a bit tedious if you already have a good understanding of Excel.
